3040 ' TANK UP
3050 DATA 24,24,219,255,255,255,255,195
3060 ' TANK DOWN
3070 DATA 195,255,255,255,255,219,24,24
3080 ' TANK LEFT
3090 DATA 63,63,30,254,254,30,63,63
3100 ' TANK RIGHT
